OUR MISSION  
About Neo Pulse Clinics  
Healthcare That Comes to You  
Community-Centred Care  
Neo Pulse Clinics brings trusted, doctor-led primary  
healthcare directly into gated residential communities across  
Bangalore. We believe quality medical care should be  
accessible, ethical, and convenient - not miles away when you  
need it most.  
By setting up clinics inside residential communities, we  
reduce the stress of travel, long waiting times, and impersonal  
consultations. Our doctors know your health history,  
understand your lifestyle, and provide care tailored to your  
family's needs.  
Our focus is on early intervention, preventive care, and  
building lasting relationships with families. We're not here to  
replace hospitals, but to be your first point of contact for  
health concerns, wellness guidance, and peace of mind.  
We work closely with Resident Welfare Associations to deliver  
health camps, senior care programmes, and emergency  
preparedness - building healthier, more resilient communities  
together.

Why Choose Neo Pulse Clinics  
We combine medical expertise, community trust, and modern convenience to deliver healthcare that truly cares.  
Doctor-Led Care  
Every consultation is led by qualified MBBS doctors with years of clinical experience and a commitment to ethical practice.  
Located Inside Communities  
No need to travel far or wait in crowded hospitals quality healthcare is just steps away from your home.  
Transparent Pricing  
Clear, upfront costs with no hidden charges. Our membership plans make quality care affordable and predictable.  
Preventive Healthcare Focus  
We emphasise early detection, lifestyle management, and wellness keeping you healthy before problems arise.  
Elderly-Friendly Services  
Special attention to senior citizens with mobility support, home visits, and care coordination for chronic conditions.  
Continuity of Care  
Your doctor knows your medical history, family health patterns, and personal preferences building trust over time.

FOR RWAS  
Community Health Partnership  
Long-Term Health Partner for Your Community  
Neo Pulse Clinics collaborates with Resident Welfare Associations to bring  
comprehensive healthcare support directly into your residential  
community with no financial burden on the RWA.  
We conduct regular health camps, preventive screenings, and wellness  
awareness programmes. Our clinics provide a trusted first point of contact  
for medical concerns, reducing the need for external hospital visits for  
routine care.  
For senior citizens, we offer specialised support including chronic disease  
management, mobility assistance, and emergency coordination. During  
health emergencies, our on-ground presence ensures faster response  
times and immediate care.  
By partnering with us, your community gains a dedicated healthcare ally  
that adds long-term value, promotes wellness, and builds a culture of  
proactive health management.  
Connect to Neo Pulse Clinic  
How It Works  
Setting up Neo Pulse Clinics in your community is simple, collaborative, and designed for long-term impact.  
Community Onboarding  
Health Camp & Interaction  
We meet with RWA representatives to understand  
community needs, demographics, and health priorities.  
We conduct an introductory health camp to meet residents,  
assess common health concerns, and build trust.  
Clinic Setup  
Ongoing Care & Support  
We establish a fully equipped clinic inside the community  
premises, staffed by qualified doctors and healthcare  
professionals.  
Residents receive continuous primary care, preventive  
health services, emergency support, and wellness  
programmes year-round.  
COMMON QUESTIONS  
Frequently Asked Questions  
Is membership mandatory?  
Will Neo Pulse Clinics replace hospitals?  
No. Membership is completely voluntary. Non-members  
can still access our services at regular consultation rates.  
Membership simply offers greater value and convenience  
for families seeking regular care.  
No. We are your first point of contact for primary care,  
preventive health, and minor emergencies. For complex  
conditions, surgeries, or specialised treatment, we  
coordinate referrals to trusted hospitals and specialists.  
Who are the doctors at Neo Pulse Clinics?  
Is my health data secure?  
All our doctors are qualified MBBS professionals with  
years of clinical experience. They are registered with the  
Medical Council of India and committed to ethical,  
patient-centred care.  
Yes. We maintain digital health records with strict data  
privacy protocols. Your medical information is encrypted,  
securely stored, and accessible only to you and your  
treating doctor.  
What areas do you serve in Bangalore?  
Can I consult online?  
We currently partner with gated residential communities  
across Bangalore. If your community is interested, we'd be  
happy to discuss a partnership. Contact us to explore  
possibilities.  
Yes. We offer both in-clinic and online consultations for  
your convenience. Digital consultations are ideal for  
follow-ups, prescription refills, and non-emergency  
health queries.
